OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779196276
OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FIt's been a busy month for the flag
OL,7,Fraisers in Beijing.
OL,9,FPresident Xi's been playing 'host with
OL,10,Fthe most' and it will reach a peak
OL,11,Fthis week, when the American stars and
OL,12,Fstripes that were fluttering around
OL,13,FTiananmen square last week are
OL,14,Freplaced by the Russian tricolour.
OL,16,FPresident Putin arrives in the Chinese
OL,17,Fcapital, just four days after Donald
OL,18,FTrump departed. The timing wasn't
OL,19,Fintentional, the summit with Trump was
OL,20,Fdelayed from March after the US and
OL,21,FIsrael launched another war on Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
