OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779196276
OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBut the Chinese leader might like how
OL,12,Fthe timing has turned out, with state
OL,13,Fmedia claiming the back-to-back
OL,14,Fmeetings show Beijing is ''fast
OL,15,Femerging as the focal point of global
OL,16,Fdiplomacy".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
