FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779196276
OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FIn Russian statements ahead of the
OL,7,Fvisit, officials were quoted stressing
OL,8,Fthe decades long, deep, profound, even
OL,9,F''precious'' relations enjoyed between
OL,10,FChina and Russia. President Xi was
OL,11,Fdescribed by Putin in a video released
OL,12,Fbefore his arrival as a his ''long-
OL,13,Ftime good friend".
OL,15,FGet the message? These two leaders
OL,16,Fhave been buddies for ages, they've
OL,17,Fmet more than forty times, this is
OL,18,FPutin's 25th visit to China. Last week
OL,19,Fwas Trump's second. He followed a tour
OL,20,Fwell-trodden by the Russian leader.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779196276
OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FThey were friends long before Trump
OL,7,Fcame on the scene and during the four
OL,8,Fyears that Trump was out of office, Xi
OL,9,FJinping and Vladimir Putin remained in
OL,10,Fpower and will likely do so beyond
OL,11,Fthis second Trump term.
OL,13,FIt's not just a shared determination
OL,14,Fto end American hegemony, but as the
OL,15,Fdirect result of some US policies that
OL,16,FChina and Russia have formed such a
OL,17,Fclose partnership.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779196276
OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FThe most recent example being the war
OL,7,Fon Iran, which has pushed Chinese
OL,8,Fpurchases of Russian oil to record
OL,9,Flevels. Imports of Russian oil are up
OL,10,Fby around thirty-five per cent this
OL,11,Fyear, now accounting for a fifth of
OL,12,FChina's crude oil imports.
OL,14,FThe war in Ukraine has rattled Russia
OL,15,Fmore, and for longer, than Putin
OL,16,Fanticipated. Major cracks are starting
OL,17,Fto appear in the economy and his
OL,18,F''military operation".
OL,26,@zD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
