PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779196276
OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FThe Russian leader is coming to
OL,7,FBeijing hoping to secure a deal for a
OL,8,Fsecond gas pipeline to which Xi has
OL,9,Fbeen reluctant to commit.
OL,11,FThe Power of Siberia 2 would bring gas
OL,12,Ffrom Russia, through Mongolia, to
OL,13,FChina and, as its name suggests, would
OL,14,Fbe the second such major pipeline
OL,15,Fbetween the two countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779196276
OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FTrade between the two countries has
OL,7,Freached record levels since the
OL,8,FRussian invasion of Ukraine in 2022.
OL,9,FIn that period China has bought $370
OL,10,Fbillion worth of Russian fossil fuels,
OL,11,Fbecoming an economic lifeline for
OL,12,FMoscow.
OL,14,FBeijing has been stalling on the
OL,15,Fsecond pipeline project, not wanting
OL,16,Fto commit to the price and to gas for
OL,17,Fits future energy supply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779196276
OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FThe war in Iran and the blockage of
OL,7,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, may have made an
OL,8,Foverland source more attractive and
OL,9,Fthe prospect of a deal more likely.
OL,11,FIt would be a major coup for Putin to
OL,12,Fcome to Beijing and sign something
OL,13,Fconcrete after the vague outcomes of
OL,14,FTrumps visit last week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
