PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779196276
OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FIn fact, the agenda suggests that
OL,7,Fthere will be 40 documents signed by
OL,8,FXi and Putin during their meetings on
OL,9,FWednesday. There was no such signing
OL,10,Fceremony when Trump was here last
OL,11,Fweek, his signature sharpie didn't get
OL,12,Fan airing in Beijing.
OL,14,FThe last time President Putin visited
OL,15,FBeijing he attended a military parade
OL,16,Fto mark the end of the second World
OL,17,FWar. We heard him and Xi, together
OL,18,Fwith Kim Jong Un, musing on
OL,19,Fimmortality, living to one hundred and
OL,20,Ffifty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
