OL,3,CPutin to meet 'long-time friend' Xi in
OL,4,CBeijing, just days after Trump visit
OL,6,FLet's hope it's the same person in
OL,7,Fcharge of the mics on this visit, and
OL,8,Fwe get to hear what Xi and Putin
OL,9,Fdiscuss while touring the state garden
OL,10,Fwhere Trump marvelled at trees older
OL,11,Fthan the United States.
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
